<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Southern_Sami_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Syntax">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Syntax">Syntax</span></h2>
<p>Unlike the other <a href="/wiki/Sami_languages" title="Sami languages">Sami languages</a>, Southern Sami is an <a href="/wiki/Subject_Object_Verb" title="Subject Object Verb">SOV language</a>.</p>
